    "description": "<h4>Required Heroic Skill: Comet</h4><p>You rip open a large portal to the Cosmos, calling down astral debris from the gaping void. Choose one option: one creature you can see suffers @DMG[60 untyped] damage; or you choose any number of creatures you can see, and each of them suffers @DMG[40 untyped] damage. These amounts increase by 5 if you are <strong>level 20 or higher</strong>, or by 10 if you are <strong>level 40 or higher</strong>. Damage dealt by this spell has no type (thus being unaffected by damage Affinities).</p><hr /><ul><li><p><strong>Target Loses:</strong> @DMG[60+&amp;step(0,5,10) untyped]{60|65|70 untyped (single)}, or @DMG[40+&amp;step(0,5,10) untyped]{40|45|50 untyped (multi)}</p></li></ul>",
